Package ibbt.sumo.sampleevaluators.datasets

Interface Summary
Dataset Interface class that contains functions that a datset should support
 

Class Summary
DatasetSampleEvaluator This class implements a dataset lookup sample evaluator.
GriddedDataset A gridded dataset contains of a single column of data, the inputvalues can be obtained by the relative position of the row
GriddedDatasetIterator class that can iterate over a gridded dataset
GriddedDatasetSampleEvaluator This class implements a gridded dataset lookup sample evaluator.

ScatteredDataset A scattered dataset contains of a series of unsorted columns of data
ScatteredDatasetSampleEvaluator This class implements a scattered dataset lookup sample evaluator.
